                    <li>3 medium yellow onions, thinly sliced</li>
                    <li>1 tablespoon balsamic vinegar</li>
                    <li>1-2 tablespoons olive oil, for brushing on top</li>
                    <li>1o ounces brie, cut into cubes (scrape rind off with a paring knife if desired, though it's not necessary)</li>
                    <li>11/2 cup fresh or frozen cranberries</li>
                   </ul> 
